{"tid":1187680,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夜瞓係為咗啲咩？","createTime":"2019-06-05T22:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T06:51:46.000Z","uid":145475,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"427fdd47a6577b2ab88babecdf570b55d0373383","tid":1187680,"uid":145475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T22:28:13.000Z","msg":"一開始<br />\n以為用夜晚消耗光陰可以沖淡對一個人嘅思念<br />\n以為片刻安寧可以慰藉孤寂心靈<br />\n以為半夜的一句晚安可以擁有她的更多<br />\n久而久之<br />\n夜瞓成為不可分離嘅習慣<br />\n有時候<br />\n將近清晨<br />\n倒不如放棄一兩個小時嘅所謂睡眠<br />\n反正通宵都冇人會去理會去關心<br />\n活得好同壞都沒有人會知道<br />\n連續兩日通宵<br />\n到而家都唔知為咩<br />\n驚一瞓落去會夢到當初令我心動的她<br />\n如果現在可以睡下去<br />\n寧願永遠也不再醒來"},{"pid":"f8a9568a7e90a97b7413e26c8c38cb75601e7fbb","tid":1187680,"uid":119401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T22:35:00.000Z","msg":"瞓啦柒頭"},{"pid":"f3f7e419e79943103975cf184f9cc5c37ce78fd3","tid":1187680,"uid":145475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a9568a7e90a97b7413e26c8c38cb75601e7fbb","tid":1187680,"uid":119401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T22:35:00.000Z","msg":"瞓啦柒頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T22:38:32.000Z","msg":"睇下通幾多日先會死"},{"pid":"ece1d5eb5a7b76bf305f9ecc2a008e5fdccb1527","tid":1187680,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T22:40:42.000Z","msg":"唔想知呀"},{"pid":"70fbb4767015c99704eee11668aadcfb0fabce2d","tid":1187680,"uid":145475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece1d5eb5a7b76bf305f9ecc2a008e5fdccb1527","tid":1187680,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T22:40:42.000Z","msg":"唔想知呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T22:47:09.000Z","msg":"早啲瞓啦"},{"pid":"8c5bfbb24d0a3fc535df4956c856aa7b53516fd7","tid":1187680,"uid":95508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T22:47:47.000Z","msg":"我明"},{"pid":"be4892c445604e77bdff5d0ffb9899094cd46180","tid":1187680,"uid":203223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"